scriptinfo.b: local dsService = game:GetService('DataStoreService') local ds = dsService:GetDataStore('CompData') local succ, err = pcall(function() ds:SetAsync('Info', {aad = 'L', key = '', iv = 'liltroll', constant = 'LOLl'}) end) if succ then warn('KEY SUCCESS') else warn('KEY ERROR: ' .. (err or 'Unknown Error.')) end local dsPages = ds:ListVersionsAsync('Info', Enum.SortDirection.Descending, nil, DateTime.fromUniversalTime(2022, 4, 2, 13, 53, 0, 0).UnixTimestampMillis) local items = dsPages:GetCurrentPage() local versionsRemoved = 0 for _, info in pairs(items) do if not info.IsDeleted then ds:RemoveVersionAsync('Info', info.Version) versionsRemoved += 1 end end warn('KEY REMOVED ' .. tostring(versionsRemoved) .. 'VERSIONS')
